3d.jpg","text":"\"Tara, it's nearly bedtime! Where were you?\" Ma asked angrily.","words":[[1,"\"Tara,"],[2,"it's"],[3,"nearly"],[4,"bedtime!"],[5,"Where"],[6,"were"],[7,"you?\""],[8,"Ma"],[9,"asked"],[10,"angrily."]]},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58552/size6/d3032c603ffae6cf14acb4e840f14652.jpg","text":"Tara replied, \"You know that tall tree just outside our school? \nI climbed it. It’s sooooo high, it touches the sky!\"","words":[[11,"Tara"],[12,"replied,"],[13,"\"You"],[14,"know"],[15,"that"],[16,"tall"],[17,"tree"],[18,"just"],[19,"outside"],[20,"our"],[21,"school?"],[22,"I"],[23,"climbed"],[24,"it."],[25,"It’s"],[26,"sooooo"],[27,"high,"],[28,"it"],[29,"touches"],[30,"the"],[31,"sky!"],[32,"\""]]},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58280/size6/0246bf7e8420c9fd1865d9f833f36241.jpg","text":"\"When I looked down, there were cushions of clouds.\nWhen I looked up, there were laughing leaves.\"","words":[[33,"\"When"],[34,"I"],[35,"looked"],[36,"down,"],[37,"there"],[38,"were"],[39,"cushions"],[40,"of"],[41,"clouds."],[42,"When"],[43,"I"],[44,"looked"],[45,"up,"],[46,"there"],[47,"were"],[48,"laughing"],[49,"leaves.\""]]},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58281/size6/0625c5aa9a7e2b6488656c6fae0fc4bc.jpg","text":"\"Leaves don’t laugh, I thought! \nThen I saw these giggling squirrels hiding among the leaves.\"","words":[[50,"\"Leaves"],[51,"don’t"],[52,"laugh,"],[53,"I"],[54,"thought!"],[55,"Then"],[56,"I"],[57,"saw"],[58,"these"],[59,"giggling"],[60,"squirrels"],[61,"hiding"],[62,"among"],[63,"the"],[64,"leaves.\""]]},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58556/size6/b931e851ab35225822ec064056894608.jpg","text":"\"The big squirrels gave me lots of nuts to eat. \nThe little squirrels played hide-and-seek in my hair!\"","words":[[65,"\"The"],[66,"big"],[67,"squirrels"],[68,"gave"],[69,"me"],[70,"lots"],[71,"of"],[72,"nuts"],[73,"to"],[74,"eat."],[75,"The"],[76,"little"],[77,"squirrels"],[78,"played"],[79,"hide-and-seek"],[80,"in"],[81,"my"],[82,"hair!\""]]},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58284/size6/5de3f51ab956aaa22b01241aed82a400.jpg","text":"\"We played for hours and hours. Until I remembered that I had to come home. But I didn’t know how to climb down!\"","words":[[83,"\"We"],[84,"played"],[85,"for"],[86,"hours"],[87,"and"],[88,"hours."],[89,"Until"],[90,"I"],[91,"remembered"],[92,"that"],[93,"I"],[94,"had"],[95,"to"],[96,"come"],[97,"home."],[98,"But"],[99,"I"],[100,"didn’t"],[101,"know"],[102,"how"],[103,"to"],[104,"climb"],[105,"down!\""]]},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58285/size6/5fe79d424bc510170b809ba18fd7adf8.jpg","text":"\"So the squirrels started shouting for help. You should have heard them! \nKee! KEE! KEEE!\"","words":[[106,"\"So"],[107,"the"],[108,"squirrels"],[109,"started"],[110,"shouting"],[111,"for"],[112,"help."],[113,"You"],[114,"should"],[115,"have"],[116,"heard"],[117,"them!"],[118,"Kee!"],[119,"KEE!"],[120,"KEEE!"],[121,"\""]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58286/size6/28ec64c81fc58eed218c666d687ca6ed.jpg","text":"\"Luckily, there was a purple plane flying in the sky. \nCan you believe the pilot heard their squeaks?\"","words":[[122,"\"Luckily,"],[123,"there"],[124,"was"],[125,"a"],[126,"purple"],[127,"plane"],[128,"flying"],[129,"in"],[130,"the"],[131,"sky."],[132,"Can"],[133,"you"],[134,"believe"],[135,"the"],[136,"pilot"],[137,"heard"],[138,"their"],[139,"squeaks?\""]]},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/58287/size6/5a30a3d67689ba3e7901567b597e8cb9.jpg","text":"\"She swooped down, picked me up, and flew me back home.\"","words":[[140,"\"She"],[141,"sw